'''Access Computer College''' (Access Computer and Technical College) is a [[Bachelor's degree|degree]]-awarding [[tertiary education]]al institution that specializes in computer and [[Vocational education|technical-vocational courses]]. Based in the [[Philippines]],''' Access Computer College '''currently have 10 campuses:''' ACCESS-Manila, ACCESS-Monumento, ACCESS-Cubao, ACCESS-Lagro, ACCESS-Camarin, ACCESS-Novaliches-Zabarte, ACCESS-Pasig, ACCESS-Marilao, ACCESS-Meycauayan, and ACCESS-Balagtas. '''<ref>{{cite web|title=Campuses |url=http://access.edu.ph/campuses.php |publisher=Access Computer College |accessdate=1 October 2012 |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6B5prxN2d?url=http://access.edu.ph/campuses.php |archivedate=1 October 2012 |deadurl=no |df= }}</ref> It was founded in 1981.<ref>{{cite web|title=About Us |url=http://access.edu.ph/aboutus.php |publisher=Access Computer College |accessdate=1 October 2012 |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6B5rFYeGL?url=http://access.edu.ph/aboutus.php |archivedate=1 October 2012 |deadurl=no |df= }}</ref>
